data.horoscope_data: Get ready to dive into the rest of spring on a social note now that Neptune is in Aries and your friendship zone. The next several weeks can bring friends into your world from all walks of life. While this can be an exciting time, Gemini, make sure you know who your real friends are.Working hard at your career could change your life when Saturn in Pisces sextiles Uranus in Taurus on Friday. Making subtle changes to your thought process can help you get ahead. Whether you’re working late or changing jobs, focus on the future.End the week on a positive note when the sun in Aries sextiles Jupiter in your sign on Sunday. This aspect brings plenty of opportunities for fun and excitement. Whether you’re making new friends at a party or networking at an event, this is your lucky day for success.
